thumb.title: Katie Ward Photography
thumb.description: Katie Ward is a photojournalist turned family photographer. She was mentored by Burt Glinn, the former CEO of Magnum. Her goal in photographing your family is to provide you the kind of warmth and energy and magical photos that she does with her own family; and to provide you with images that you and your family will cherish for a lifetime.Katie Ward PhotographyNew York City917-842-7849https://www.katie-ward.com/
